* Zendo no Masada (善道真貞) – {{ill|Shōgoi|ja|正五位}} Lower, Governor of {{ill|Awa Province|ja|阿波国}}
* Okiwara Toshihisa (興原敏久) – {{ill|Shōgoi|ja|正五位}} Upper, Senior Judge of {{ill|Gyōbushō|ja|刑部省}}
* Fujiwara no Mamoru (藤原衛) – {{ill|Jūshii|ja|従四位}} Lower, Vice Minister of {{ill|Gyōbushō|ja|刑部省}}
* Fujiwara no Uton (藤原雄敏) – {{ill|Jūshii|ja|従四位}} Lower, Senior Official of {{ill|Kageyushō|ja|勘解由使}}
* {{ill|Sugawara no Kiyokimi|ja|菅原清公}} – {{ill|Shōshii|ja|正四位}} Lower, {{ill|Left Kyoto District Governor|ja|左京大夫}}
* {{ill|Fujiwara no Tsunatsugu|ja|藤原常嗣}} – {{ill|Jūshii|ja|従四位}} Lower, {{ill|Councilor|ja|参議}}
* Minabuchi no Hirozane (南淵弘貞) – {{ill|Jūsanmi|ja|従三位}}, Councilor
* {{ill|Kiyohara no Natsuno|ja|清原夏野}} – {{ill|Shōsanmi|ja|正三位}}, {{ill|Udaijin|ja|右大臣}}

