* Kawakare Katsunari (川枯勝成) – {{ill|Jūhachi-i|ja|従八位|1=Junior Eighth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} U11er, Minor Official of {{ill|Gyōbushō|ja|刑部省|12=draft|12=draft}}
* {{ill|Sanuki no Emanari|ja|讃岐永直|12=draft|12=draft}} – {{ill|Jūrokui|ja|従六位|1=Junior Sixth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, Left Recorder, {{ill|Myōbōhakase|ja|明法博士|12=draft|12=draft}}
* {{ill|Ono no Takamura|ja|小野篁|12=draft|12=draft}} – {{ill|Jūgoin|ja|従五位|1=Junior Fifth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, Minor Governor of {{ill|Dazaifu|ja|大宰府|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Zendo no Masada (善道真貞) – {{ill|Shōgoi|ja|正五位|1=Senior Fifth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, Governor of {{ill|Awa Province|ja|阿波国|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Okiwara Toshihisa (興原敏久) – {{ill|Shōgoi|ja|正五位|1=Senior Fifth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} U11er, Senior Judge of {{ill|Gyōbushō|ja|刑部省|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Fujiwara no Mamoru (藤原衛) – {{ill|Jūshii|ja|従四位|1=Junior Fourth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, Vice Minister of {{ill|Gyōbushō|ja|刑部省|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Fujiwara no Uton (藤原雄敏) – {{ill|Jūshii|ja|従四位|1=Junior Fourth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, Senior Official of {{ill|Kageyushō|ja|勘解由使|12=draft|12=draft}}
* {{ill|Sugawara no Kiyokimi|ja|菅原清公|12=draft|12=draft}} – {{ill|Shōshii|ja|正四位|1=Senior Fourth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, {{ill|Left Kyoto District Governor|ja|左京大夫|12=draft|12=draft}}
