* {{ill|Sanuki no Emanari|ja|讃岐永直|12=draft|12=draft}} – {{ill|Jūrokui|ja|従六位|1=Junior Sixth Rank|12=draft|12=draft}} Lower, Left Recorder, {{ill|Myōbōhakase|ja|明法博士|12=draft|12=draft}}
