* {{ill|Ono no Takamura|ja|小野篁|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ono no Takamura|qq=}} – {{ill|Jūgoin|ja|従五位|1=Junior Fifth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jūgoin|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank|qq=}} Lower, Minor Governor of {{ill|Dazaifu|ja|大宰府|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dazaifu|qq=}}
* Zendo no Masada (善道真貞) – {{ill|Shōgoi|ja|正五位|1=Senior Fifth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōgoi|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=}} Lower, Governor of {{ill|Awa Province|ja|阿波国|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Awa Province|qq=}}
* Okiwara Toshihisa (興原敏久) – {{ill|Shōgoi|ja|正五位|1=Senior Fifth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōgoi|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=}} U11er, Senior Judge of {{ill|Gyōbushō|ja|刑部省|1=Ministry of Justice (pre-modern Japan)|lt=Ministry of Justice|qq= (pre-modern Japan)|1=Ministry of Justice (pre-modern Japan)|lt=Ministry of Justice|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gyōbushō|13=User:Immanuelle/Ministry of Justice (pre-modern Japan)|qq=}}
