rth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jūshii|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=}} Lower, Senior Official of {{ill|Kageyushō|ja|勘解由使|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kageyushō|qq=}} * [[:en:Sugawara no Kiyotomo|Sugawara no Kiyokimi]] – {{ill|Shōshii|ja|正四位|1=Senior Fourth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōshii|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fourth Rank|qq=}} Lower, {{ill|Left Kyoto District Governor|ja|左京大夫|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Left Kyoto District Governor|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 京職}} * [[:en:Fujiwara no Tsunetsugu|Fujiwara no Tsunatsugu]] – {{ill|Jūshii|ja|従四位|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jūshii|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=}} Lower, [[:en:Sangi (Japan)|Sangi]] * Minabuchi no Hirozane (南淵弘貞) – {{ill|Jūsanmi|ja|従三位|1=Junior Third Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jūsanmi|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Third Rank|qq=}}, Councilor * {{ill|Kiyohara no Natsuno|ja|清原夏野|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyohara no Natsuno|qq=}} – {{ill|Shōsanmi|ja|正三位|1=Senior Third Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōsanmi|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Third Rank|qq=}}, [[:en:Minister of the Right|Udaijin]]
